The paper proposes a new encryption scheme for images, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The paper also introduces a new non-parametric test for pixel randomness, which involves statistical analysis (cs.IT). The encryption scheme is applied to images, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and computer vision (cs.CV) categories. The paper also discusses the strength of the encryption scheme, which involves assessing security, a topic that falls under the category of social and information networks (cs.SI).
